These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-1::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, banana, cucumber, papaya
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, electronic, house, r&b
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, architect, lawyer, entrepreneur
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water, milk, cola
 1. the person drinking water is the fan of electronic##1
 2. the person eating cucumber is the fan of house##1
 3. the journalist is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 4. the architect is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 5. the person eating banana is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
 8. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the left of the fan of house##5
 9. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
10. the entrepreneur is somewhere to the right of the lawyer##5
11. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person eating papaya##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |    4     |
| Food          | papaya     | banana   | apple | cucumber |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | blues    | r&b   | house    |
| Job           | lawyer       | entrepreneur   | architect   | journalist     |
| Beverage     | water       | almond-milk | cola  | milk      |

