.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-2::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, billiard, snooker, canasta
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, volleyball, soccer, baseball
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, goldfish
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, roller, scooter, skateboard
 1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
 2. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
 3. the owner of the goldfish is the person playing monopoly##1
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5
 5. the person playing snooker is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 6. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person playing billiard##2
 8. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
 9. the owner of the dog is the person who's sport is baseball##1
10. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
11. the person driving the car is on the left of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |      4       |
| Game      | billiard       | monopoly | canasta     | snooker     |
| Sport   | volleyball      | surfing       | baseball | soccer |
| Pet           | frog       | goldfish    | dog     | bird         |
| Transport     | skateboard | scooter     | car     | roller       |

