.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, chess, drawing, collecting
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, horror, martial-arts, satire
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, hip-hop, rock, techno
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, fonseca, davidoff, vegafina
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 2. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
 3. the fan of blues is somewhere to the right of the fan of hip-hop##5
 4. the fan of techno is somewhere to the right of the vegafina-smoker##5
 5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 6. the vegafina-smoker is between the fan of techno and the fan of rock##2
 7. the fan of blues is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 8. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere to the left of the fonseca-smoker##5
 9. the pall-mall-smoker is in an even position##4
10. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the person watching martial-arts movies is the pall-mall-smoker##1
12. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |    4    |
| Hobby          | collecting    | drawing      | chess   | woodworking |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | martial-arts | horror | satire  |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | rock         | blues  | techno  |
| Cigar           | davidoff      | pall-mall          | vegafina | fonseca  |

