.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, mirinda, sprite
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, ebony, blue, coral
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, jet-ski, trike, bike
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, handball, lacrosse, tennis
 1. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the left of the person who likes blood-red##5
 2. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
 3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who likes blue##3
 4. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
 5. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
 7. the person drinking mirinda is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person drinking sprite##2
 8. the person who likes ebony is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
10. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
11. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
13. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the left of the person who likes blood-red##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |       3        |      4      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | cola     | mirinda        | sprite      |
| Color           | ebony    | coral   | blue | blood-red |
| Transport   | bike      | jet-ski    | quad-bike        | trike         |
| Sport         | baseball    | lacrosse | tennis         | handball    |

