 9. the chef is somewhere to the right of the person playing bridge##5
10. the person playing chess is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3
12. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
13. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5

