 1. the project-manager is somewhere to the right of the person who growsrose##5
 2. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 3. the accountant is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the project-manager##2
 4. the person who growsbellflower is somewhere to the left of the project-manager##5
 5. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who growszinnia##3
 6. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
 7. the doctor is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 8. the person who growssunflower is somewhere to the right of the analyst##5
 9. the doctor is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
10. the accountant is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
11. the townhouse house is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
12. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3      |        4        |
| Beverage      | water   | hot-chocolate | iced-tea   | sprite          |
| Flower          | bellflower    | rose        | zinnia     | sunflower          |
| Job           | analyst | doctor        | accountant | project-manager |
| House   | wooden    | cape-cod     | townhouse      | ranch-style        |

