.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, water
City: london, miami, berlin, venice
4 different pets are kept: ferret, mouse, cat, guinea-pig
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, skateboard, snowmobile, taxi
 1. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 3. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
 4. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 5. the person traveling to miami is between the person traveling to berlin and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
 6. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
 7. the person traveling to berlin is the owner of the mouse##1
 8. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
10. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
11. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
13. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | water      | hot-chocolate | coffee     |
| City           | venice   | london  | miami        | berlin |
| Pet   | ferret     | guinea-pig     | cat      | mouse   |
| Transport     | skateboard | snowmobile | taxi          | roller     |

