.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, lime, tomato, watermelon
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, mechanic, social-worker, teacher
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, rowing, baseball, climbing
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, ivory, white, lavender
 1. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rowing##5
 2. the person who likes lavender is the person eating blueberry##1
 3. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the left of the person who likes purple##5
 4. the architect is in an even position##4
 5. the mechanic is on the left of the person who likes white##1
 6. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the right of the person who likes ivory##5
 7. the social-worker is the person who's sport is climbing##1
 8. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the left of the architect##5
 9. the person who likes white is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
10. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the right of the person eating tomato##5
11. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
12. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the left of the person eating tomato##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | blueberry | tomato  | watermelon    | lime       |
| Job           | mechanic  | teacher | social-worker | architect  |
| Sport   | rowing    | baseball   | climbing  | badminton     |
| Color   | lavender      | white    | ivory        | purple |

 